  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the parents of Lillian, at the time being in ghetto, Warsaw ghetto, they got the message from Morefski that they should come to join him in Grodno, to-- to go through the border and go on the side of the Russian occupation.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, the parents of Lillian decided that she will go there with her aunt, because the-- the parents of Lillian, they could not go because at that time, her-- her mother was still alive, and they don't-- didn't want to abandon her-- their mother.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it was mother of-- of father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they stayed ghetto, and also the-- the little child, sister of Lillian was there too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So only Lillian and this aunt went through illegal ways, through the-- we call it the green border, which means they hired somebody to-- to cross the River Bug on the other side, to go to the Russians, to the Russian occupation region.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- they-- finally, they reached the city Grodno.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this city, Grodno, she was living there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But meantime, not-- not long after, Morefski had to go to, I think, to Smolensk, to other city in Russia because he was performing in the territories.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so-- and Lillian was at that time in school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she was finishing the school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she was exposed already to Soviet Union and-- and-- and the life in the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as the young person, she didn't understand politics and everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And not everything was known at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she was quite a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- I can't say-- well, not hostile to the Russians, which was a different from Polish people who were in-- in the occupied by Soviets part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were always hostile to Russia, to the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
